data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT AND MOTIVATED SELLER on this WONDERFULLY laid out 3 bed 2 bath home meticulously maintained! IMPROVEMENTS include: 2020 - HVAC, garage door, carpet in living & dining, freshly painted board on board fence; 2021 - SS appliances; & 2017 - Roof & gutters; 2022 - water heater. This home offers open floor plan with high ceilings, beautiful arches & attention to detail. Split bedroom floor plan with spacious secondary bedrooms. Open kitchen & living features wood burning fireplace with gas start! Spacious master features walk in closet, garden tub, separate shower & extra long vanity with dual sinks! Back yard features a HUGE covered patio with ceiling fans, storage shed, board on board fence & driveway has been extended for extra parking! Hidden Creek community offers clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, ponds & sand volleyball. Convenient walking distance to City Lake Park, Elementary & Middle School.  Furniture & other items available for purchase making it one turn key!
